Create your Slack Workspace Step: Create your Slack Workspace Create a Slack workspace by going to https://slack.com/get-started#/createnew and logging in with an email which is not your IBM email. Your IBM email is part of the IBM Slack enterprise account and you will not be able to create an independent Slack workspace outside if the IBM slack service.
After authentication, you will see the following screen:
Click Create a Workspace -&gt;
